settings.accordian_title_1: how do i decide which style of jean will fit me best?
settings.text_1: there are a hundred different ways to wear our jeans, and each person’s body and style can affect what they choose. that’s what we love about denim! but, we know it can be a bit overwelming to choose your first pair. we recommend taking a look at the size and fit sections of each item to get a sense of how the jean fits, but we’re always here to help. please call us at (615) 739 5286 or email us at help@imogeneandwillie.com if you’d like help with a fit or style recommendation.
